sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor Admin
    participant UI as UI
    participant SR as support_routes.py
    participant EH as entry_handler.py
    participant KI as knowledge_ingestion.py
    participant BL as blob_storage.py
    participant AZB as Azure Blob
    participant EM as embeddings.py
    participant AZE as Azure OpenAI
    participant VS as AzureSearch VectorStore
    participant AZS as Azure AI Search

    Admin->>UI: upload .docx / .pptx / .pdf
    UI->>SR: POST /entry/knowledge multipart/form-data
    Note over SR: handle_knowledge_upload() L121
    Note over SR: data = await file.read() L123
    SR->>EH: upload_knowledge(filename, data) L126

    EH->>KI: upload_document(filename, data) L84
    Note over KI: _get_knowledge_store() L26
    Note over KI: AzureSearch(knowledge_index_v2)

    KI->>BL: upload_file(filename, data) L29
    BL->>AZB: upload_blob(filename, data)
    AZB-->>BL: ok
    BL-->>KI: confirmed

    KI->>KI: _extract_text(data, content_type) L513
    alt .docx
        Note over KI: Document(BytesIO(data))
    else .pptx
        Note over KI: Presentation(BytesIO(data))
    else .pdf
        KI->>KI: _extract_pdf_text() L563
    end

    KI->>KI: _split_into_sections() L188
    Note over KI: _detect_cosolve_phase() L363
    Note over KI: _build_small_chunks() L440

    KI->>KI: delete_by_source(filename) L53
    Note over KI: removes existing docs

    loop for each chunk
        KI->>KI: _build_doc_id() L509
        KI->>KI: build metadata
    end

    KI->>EM: get_embeddings() L19
    Note over EM: lru_cache singleton
    Note over EM: text-embedding-3-large

    CI->>VS: AzureSearch(knowledge_index_v2)
    KI->>AZS: add_texts(texts, metadatas, ids) L154
    Note over AZS: LangChain embeds via AZE
    AZE-->>AZS: embeddings batch
    AZS-->>KI: List[doc_id]

    KI-->>EH: chunks_indexed=N
    EH-->>SR: EntryResponseEnvelope status=accepted
    SR-->>UI: EntryResponseEnvelope
    UI-->>Admin: success
